query:
SELECT ps.id, ps.colaborador, ps.cargo, ps.planSustitucionId 
FROM planes_sucesion ps
WHERE ps.planSustitucionId IS NULL OR ps.planSustitucionId NOT IN (SELECT id FROM planes_sustitucion WHERE puestoClave = 'Si')
LIMIT 10;
